{"tid":1245054,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[向西系列] 港產片《作家的謊言》有冇人會睇？","createTime":"2019-06-20T07:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T05:07:10.000Z","uid":15213,"like":16,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4dabe6dc4c2851e76ef9d3d1d3df701f6628f82a","tid":1245054,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"今日上畫，有冇人睇咗？會睇？入嚟討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">《作家的謊言：筆忠誘罪》</span></strong></span><br />\n其實成個名有點柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrom Facebook:<br />\n一部籌備、拍攝連後期共用了三年時間的心血之作《作家的謊言：筆忠誘罪》，說不上大製作，但絕對是近年少見的高質驚慄懸疑小品，編劇、導演及演員都傾囊而出，而幾星期的優先場，觀眾一致的高度評價，給予我們一個肯定！香港電影業生存空間細，但一班憑住一腔熱血香港電影工作者，仍希望為香港人拍出優質的港產片，好的作品亦需要你們每一位入場支持！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wmoov.com/assets/movie/photo/201905/HO00000631.jpeg_1559180876.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwmoov.com%2Fassets%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201905%2FHO00000631.jpeg_1559180876.jpg&h=87537ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">簡介：</span></span><br />\n治癒系作家徐哲(張建聲 飾)同太太Jeana及兒子本來有個幸福美滿家庭，自從樓上租客情婦(松岡李那 飾)突然出現，令徐哲的美滿人生出現無法想像的變卦...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主演：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">張建聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 松岡李那 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何佩瑜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有陳嘉莉, 王宗堯, 趙永洪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 陸永, 鄭詩君, 吳岱融, 鄒文正, 方詠琳, 陳浩民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4ebae72a196a462289bf6539cbb3e9eceab134","tid":1245054,"uid":15213,"like":